
 POLLEX DOCUMENTATION
 ------------------------------
        _
       | \        
       | |___
 _____/  (___)    Pollex: from Latin 'pollex', thumb.
|o|     (_____)
|_|____	 (____)   A thumbs-up tool for collaborative teams.
       \_(___)   
 
 Pollex is a web-based application for conducing online polls.

 The software currently features

   a) multiple choice polls with varying decision criteria
   b) event scheduling consensus with priority assignments 

 User Documentation
 ------------------------------
 
 Pollex user guide can be found in file userguide.txt.

 Developer Documentation
 ------------------------------

 Directory pollex/doc/developers contains useful information for developers
 willing to contribute to the project. If this is for you, please, start
 by reading contrib.txt file.

